# KB Academy Training Session Archive and View Mode

## Purpose
Separate operational training session execution from historical record viewing.

## Changes
- training session record view is read-only
- active session runner remains interactive only for in-progress workflow
- admins can archive sessions without deleting them
- archive metadata is stored on the training session record

## Archive Fields
- archived_at
- archived_by
- archive_reason

## Rules
- archived sessions remain in history unless later filtered out
- archived sessions are never hard-deleted through the app
- viewing a session from Training Records opens a read-only record page
- viewing mode does not allow section edits, sign-off actions, or completion actions

## Future Expansion
- archive filters on Training Records
- dedicated audit trail event logging
- unarchive flow if needed